    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2) in impeccable condition. This wide-body icon features the legendary 3.6L flat-six engine delivering 315 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and an advanced all-wheel-drive system. Mechanically superior, it boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit, updated rear main seal, and a fresh water pump for ultimate peace of mind. The factory M030 sport suspension provides razor-sharp turn-in, while the Turbo-spec 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers offer exceptional thermal capacity. Finished in a flawless deep gloss with a pristine interior, this C4S exhibits zero bore scoring and a perfectly linear power band. A turnkey example for the discerning collector.",
